quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,234,"∆Āen maayoo…ďe acca suddii…ďe …ďe ronndaaki, wa…ó…óike …ďen [suddii…ďe] habbagol ko'e ma…ď…ďe lebbi nayi e bal…óe sappo, …ďe heddoo ka cuu…óii, …ďe wo…ó…óitoo cu…óaari e desal. Si edda on timmii, bakkaatu fawaaki on (yo waliyuu…ďe), e kon ko …ďe wa…óaŇčta ko'e ma…ď…ďe -e hoore laawol shari'a; immorde e …óin …ói …ďe ha…óanoo fewndo edda on. Alla No Anndi kon ko golloton, huunde e ko suu…óoton maa fee√Īinon wirnanaaki Mo. O Yo…ďoyay on …óum."
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde …ďa∆ī∆īiŇčton faale mo'on ∆īamde suddii…ďe …ďen fewndo eddinagol; wano wiide mo: si edda maa on timmii, humpitam. Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko suu…óoton faale mo'on ∆īamde …ďe si edda ma…ď…ďe on timmii. Alla No Anndi on annditoyay fii ma…ď…ďe, sa…ďu tii…óugol mon yi…óugol …ďe, O Daginani on ngol …ďa∆ī∆īingol. ReŇčtee fodondirgol ∆īamal fewndo edda; si wanaa kon ko dagorii …ďa∆ī∆īingol. Wata on humu kadi dewgal fewndo edda. Nganndee pellet Alla No Anndi kon ko suu…óoton e pittaali mo'on; immorde e ko O Dagini maa ko O Harmini, reenee e Makko, wata on lunndo Yamiroore Makko. Nganndon pellet Alla ko Haforanoowo …ďen tuuboo…ďe e jeyaa…ďe Makko, Mu√Ī√Īii…óo Mo yaawnantaako …ďe lepte."
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddii…ďe mon …ďen ado on renndidude e ma…ď…ďe,maa ado on wa…ó…óinannde …ďe teŇče heerii…óo.Si …óum wa…óii,teŇče woo alanaa…ďe;ko see…óa tan wa…ó…óii jonnugol …ďe ko …ďe dakmitora...?"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddii…ďe mon …ďen ado on renndidue, tawa on jaŇčtanike …ďe teŇče; ko feccere on teŇče wa…ó…óii jonnugol …ďe, si wanaa hara …ďe ya'afi (si …ďe hellifaa), maa moodi…ď…ďe …ďen tigiri ya'afoo jonna teŇče …óen fof. Ko ya'afondirgol haqqeeji mon …óin …ďurata …ďa…ótinde on dewal e …óoftaare Alla. Onon yim…ďe, wata on yejjitu …ďural ngal hakkunde mo'on, maa ya'afondirgol haqqeeji. Pellet Alla No Reeni kon ko golloton, tii…ónee e mo∆ī∆īere no da√Īiron mbarjaari Alla."